patthana23.39:1.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.39:1.1_1: Naanidassanasappaṭighaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.39:1.1_2: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ nakusalañca naanidassanasappaṭighaṁ nakusalañca dhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.39:2.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā anidassanaappaṭigho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.39:3.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … satta. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
